theorem Topology.interior_closure_subset_closure_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} :
    interior (closure (A : Set X)) ⊆ closure (interior (closure A)) := by
  simpa using
    (subset_closure :
      (interior (closure (A : Set X)) : Set X) ⊆
        closure (interior (closure A)))
